title: Moving Shadow 00.1 FLAC
description: 00.1 is a specially created, 10th year anniversary release, put together to mark a decade of Moving Shadow. This double CD, containing an 80 minute mix of some of Moving Shadow's most celebrated releases plus a CD ROM dedicated to the label's history, music, artists and design, is the fifth in the label's showcase series, and follows on from the '99.1' and '99.2' releases of last year.
